org.activebpel.rt.util
Class AeLRUObjectCache

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.util.AeLRUObjectCache
public class AeLRUObjectCache
extends java.lang.Object

Generic object caching. If max size is exceeded, the least recently usesd (lru) object in the cache is removed to make room for the most current.

cache

public java.lang.Object cache(java.lang.Object aNewKey,
                              java.lang.Object aNewValue)
Caches the key/value pair. If the cache is full, the oldest key/value pair in the cache will be removed and the KEY to the removed object will be returned. Otherwise, null will be returned.

Parameters:
aNewKey - The mapping key.
aNewValue - The mapping value.
Returns:
The key value of the object that was removed to make room for the new cache pair, or null if the cache is not full.
